<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nt yạ ạbn ạllh rbnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạản̊ta yā ạb̊na ạllhi rabũnā .. waḥiṣ̊nunā ạl̊manīʿ̊
 wāl̊wasīṭu wāl̊munajĩy .. wāl̊muʿazĩy wālsẖãfīʿ̊

[V2]
 2- ạản̊ta qab̊la ạl̊kẖal̊qi kun̊ta .. maj̊duka qab̊la ạldũhūr̊
 qab̊la ạản̊ yakūna gẖam̊ruⁿ .. ạảẘ yuḍīʾa ạl̊kaẘna nūr̊

[V3]
 3- kil̊maẗu ạllhi bahāʾu .. maj̊dihi waras̊muhu
 ḥāmiluⁿ likulĩ sẖaẙʾiⁿ .. lạa yuḥadũ ʿil̊muhu

[V4]
 4- ạản̊ta rā̊̉sunā wabik̊ruⁿ .. wāritẖuⁿ likulĩ sẖaẙ
 ạản̊ta rāʿīnā ạlãdẖī qad̊ .. māta wah̊wa ạlậna ḥaỹ̊

[V5]
 5- farajāʾu ạl̊maj̊di fīnā .. ạản̊ta yā kan̊za ạl̊gẖinay̱
 wakamālu kulĩ waʿ̊diⁿ .. wasurūriⁿ wamunay̱

[V6]
 6- ạản̊ta ạl̊kulũ min̊ka ạl̊kulũ .. rabũ yasūʿu ạl̊masīḥ̊
 laka minãạ kulũ sẖuk̊riⁿ .. wasujūdiⁿ wamadīḥ̊</lyrics>
</song>